_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qErhb-uKO9wQ7kNvgHDlXd3&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDvAVrfIH5qAGwtYTp-SnFJeTLdcXcR6jvJD3zRlQrhwQ&oe=66FAA8D3"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "627211022861814", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031653_627211026195147_859210511188470322_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=gLowMo0sF-UQ7kNvgFWUro0&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDRFoD2W20IWyDVCLrb1BSyDv_xl3UlEfnbn6eOktZgOg&oe=66FAA328"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "VRLegs", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Welcome to \"VRLegs\", where the thrill of parkour meets the immersive world of virtual reality. Step into a realm where your movements are fluid, intuitive, and empowering. Our state-of-the-art locomotion system redefines how you move, jump, and traverse in the VR space, offering an unparalleled sensation of freedom.\n\nChallenge friends or team up in heart-pounding multiplayer tag matches. Navigate complex terrains, leap across buildings, and experience the exhilaration of real-time chases. As you master your environment, you'll discover new strategies, shortcuts, and moves to stay one step ahead or elude capture.\n\nWhether you're a parkour enthusiast or new to the world of VR, \"VRLegs\" promises an adrenaline-pumping experience like no other. Join the revolution, find your rhythm, and let the chase begin!", "short_description": "Unleash parkour prowess in \"VRLegs\"! Dive into multiplayer tag, powered by a groundbreaking VR locomotion system. Feel the rush!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://vrlegs.xyz/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "ForkingVR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://vrlegs.xyz/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}, {"id"